snippet.title: Necesse Graphics Update Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Necesse Graphics Update is now live!

In this update we have redrawn every single asset in Necesse to give the game a fresh new look! If you'd like to read the full changelog, then check out our steam post:
https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1169040/view/4352250961656694552

If you’d like to learn more about Necesse, check out our Steam link or social media channels below.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1169040?utm_source=nsm&utm_campaign=youtube 
Discord: https://discord.gg/qU3CtRHhBw 
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Necesse/ 
X/Twitter: https://twitter.com/NecesseGame
Japanese X/Twitter: https://x.com/Necesse_jp
